name: Go Fish Master
description:
This is an easy and addicting fishing game.

Just tap to cast your line and then catch rare fish. Sell your fish to earn money.
You can upgrade your net and line. Then go deeper and catch more kinds of rare fish.

Features:
-Easy to start, try your best to catch more fish every time!
-Try to collect all kinds of fish.
-You can still earn money when offline.
